    "IoT-based healthcare using blockchainThe sensitivity of healthcare information requires strict privacy measures.",
    "The execution of blockchain in eHealth can address these concerns, enhance service efficiency, and facilitate the shift towards decentralized eHealth systems.Here is an example of how blockchain can benefit IoTbased healthcare systems.",
    "It can be represented in Fig. 11.",
    "IoT devices collect patient data, such as vital signs, medication adherence, and other health-related information.",
    "This information is then transferred to a blockchain network, which is decentralized and secure."
  ]
}